<createdBy>nuvolia</createdBy>
<createdTime>2025-10-28 11:34:05 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[‘Cash on hand’ shall include holdings of national and foreign banknotes and coins in circulation that are commonly used to make payments.

